@deffn {Function} contrib_ode (@var{eqn}, @var{y}, @var{x})

Returns a list of solutions of the ODE @var{eqn} with 
independent variable @var{x} and dependent variable @var{y}.

@opencatbox
@category{Package contrib_ode}
@closecatbox

